id: CMP-planner
kind: component
name: Planner
status: draft
conformance_level: structural
level: subsystem
path: CMP-mission-computer / CMP-planner
description: At each decision event, composes a 512x512 map image (aircraft position, heading arrow, flight trail overlaid on an OpenStreetMap tile), builds a context-aware prompt from the event type and mission context, calls the VLM inference backend (Gemma 4 E2B via llama.cpp HTTP API), parses the JSON response, stores the scratchpad fields (progress, next_intent), and returns an RTL command on any failure.
parent: CMP-mission-computer
satisfies: REQ-reasoning-logged, REQ-rtl-on-parse-failure
events_scoped_here: VER-reasoning-logged, VER-rtl-on-parse-failure
